<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='405000' id='t-405000'>by the social and cultural norms</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='408000' id='t-408000'>of their times --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='410000' id='t-410000'>whether it be the doctors</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='412000' id='t-412000'>in Victorian England, say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='414000' id='t-414000'>who sent women to asylums</span>
