</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='432000' id='t-432000'>And what all this means</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='434000' id='t-434000'>is that paradigms</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='436000' id='t-436000'>take far too long to shift,</span>
