</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480000' id='t-480000'>And we've also got to be aware</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='482000' id='t-482000'>that experts, of course,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='484000' id='t-484000'>also make mistakes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486000' id='t-486000'>They make mistakes every single day --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='489000' id='t-489000'>mistakes born out of carelessness.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='492000' id='t-492000'>A recent study in the Archives of Surgery</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='495000' id='t-495000'>reported surgeons</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497000' id='t-497000'>removing healthy ovaries,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500000' id='t-500000'>operating on the wrong side of the brain,</span>
